{"tid":1431187,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁美芬石硤尾邨辦事處被毀　門外被黑漆噴上「老鼠BB」","createTime":"2019-08-08T02:37:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T04:57:02.000Z","uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"df0af9e16191d793c51c1dd1461adc23d744edf6","tid":1431187,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T02:37:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3124157/org/cf070daf6dbf98eedfd99fd52ef31803.jpg/p5N-0do5ignnMIdyPOquFTRR_AHmBNeHpxmvW40Zr1s?v=w1600r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3124157%2Forg%2Fcf070daf6dbf98eedfd99fd52ef31803.jpg%2Fp5N-0do5ignnMIdyPOquFTRR_AHmBNeHpxmvW40Zr1s%3Fv%3Dw1600r16_9&h=dd194614&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n修訂《逃犯條例》爭議觸發的民怨一發不可收拾，過去兩日多區連串衝穾後，今日（6日）凌晨近3時，經民聯立法會議員梁美芬位於石硤尾邨21座的辦事處遭人毀壞，門外被人用黑漆噴上「老鼠BB」字句、花盆被毀、海報遭撕毀。<br />\n<br />\n警員趕抵調查後，將案件列作「刑事毀壞」處理，現正調查事件。此外，毗鄰經民聯區議員陳國偉辦事處，亦有海報被人撕毀，警方正調查是否有關連。梁美芬中午在facebook發帖表示，該辦事處不只是屬於她一人，亦是屬於石硤尾街坊，又指這次破壞行為令一名98歲婆婆受到驚恐，以示威者常用口號be water諷刺，指「今次真係要use water同waste water」。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/360399/%E7%B6%93%E6%B0%91%E8%81%AF%E6%A2%81%E7%BE%8E%E8%8A%AC%E7%9F%B3%E7%A1%A4%E5%B0%BE%E9%82%A8%E8%BE%A6%E4%BA%8B%E8%99%95%E8%A2%AB%E6%AF%80-%E9%96%80%E5%A4%96%E8%A2%AB%E9%BB%91%E6%BC%86%E5%99%B4%E4%B8%8A-%E8%80%81%E9%BC%A0bb</code></pre>"},{"pid":"5cefdd60a2873d789a371aff76776cf9f81fdf83","tid":1431187,"uid":294052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T02:40:00.000Z","msg":"老處bb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58cb1137da927d226fa7d3be9ae2336959bde09b","tid":1431187,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:47:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91b5089c3be139e2d5ad1687b9ccad08bd81d8d2","tid":1431187,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0